products.label: Leisure

fare.label: Leisure
fare.conditions:
Refund: If ticket not used, refundable 7 days before train departure. Thereafter, no refund allowed. 

Exchanges: If ticket not used, exchangeable 7 days before train departure, then exchangeable with 15€ fees from 6 days until departure date. Thereafter, no exchange allowed.

WARNING: Please note that 3 extra business days may be needed to process the aftersales through your travel agency
